## VISUAL DESIGN
- EU choropleth map on overview page
- Key indicator numbers per country
- Country deep dive pages
- Filters and interactivity planned
- Graphics visualization to be developed

## KEY CONSTRAINTS
- User writes no code independently — AI handles all coding
- Data privacy priority → Claude (Anthropic) preferred
- Keep costs low (Streamlit Community Cloud is free)
- Context loss between sessions is main friction — this file solves that

